<genericPage guid="67e40dbb-55ff-4509-8496-ea2e7eee1f72" id="52589" nodeName="Sustainability" isDoc="" updated="2024-05-16T14:40:03.6570000Z" parentGUID="1e437ab1-de9c-402a-bf63-da580ffe1715" nodeTypeAlias="genericPage" templateAlias="GenericResponsive" sortOrder="6" published="true" isBlueprint="false">
  <bannerDropdown><![CDATA[Ski Holidays]]></bannerDropdown>
  <bodyText><![CDATA[<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><img src="/media/13102828/sustainability-hero-900.jpg" alt="SustainabilityHero" data-udi="umb://media/20975f889216458aa637fb6924ff9291" /></p>
<strong>Our Sustainability Journey - </strong>At Inghams, we’re passionate about travel, and it’s our passion that drives us to make a difference in the world. As we continue to offer activity-based holidays in the great outdoors, in some of nature’s most magnificent locations across Europe and Canada, we know it is essential that we contribute to industrywide change for a more sustainable future.</div>
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow"></div>
</div>
<div class="g12">
<div class="white_box_shadow">
<h2 style="text-align: center;">Protecting our futures</h2>
<p style="text-align: center;">Lowering our carbon footprint, participating in nature regeneration and engaging and empowering communities</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img style="width: 500px; height: 500px;" src="/media/13102832/wheel-of-impact-v6-700x700.jpg?width=500&amp;height=500" alt="WheelofImpact700x700" data-udi="umb://media/f53a7c6174864f99a1acfe68f242d151" /></p>
</div>
</div>
<h2>Climate</h2>
<p>Reducing our carbon footprint</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img style="width: 250px; height: 250px;" src="/media/13102829/transport-with-a-ticket-250x250.jpg?width=250&amp;height=250" alt="TransportTicket" data-udi="umb://media/f5593cf51b5b46ff9a839bab94060d21" /><br />
<p style="text-align: center;">Transport - Offering lower carbon <a data-udi="umb://document/599491ab41f44d11a3c4cd9f7ef48bf5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/599491ab41f44d11a3c4cd9f7ef48bf5}" title="Ski holidays by train">transport choices</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100624/accommodation-250x250-v2.jpg" alt="accommodationicon" data-udi="umb://media/9e7446f042cf414f9812f178de7544ca" />
<p style="text-align: center;">Accommodation - Working with partners to reduce their footprint.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100617/activities-250x250.jpg" alt="activityicon" data-udi="umb://media/2b7a4189e80f456693ac2522395390f4" />
<p style="text-align: center;"><span></span>Activities - Exploring <a data-udi="umb://document/f3dbae7291f94e189e126ec859efa344" href="/{localLink:umb://document/f3dbae7291f94e189e126ec859efa344}" title="Walking Holidays">lower impact</a>, nature-friendly activities.</p>
</div>
</div>
<h2>Biodiversity</h2>
<p>Contributing to nature regeneration</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100622/purchasing-250x250.jpg" alt="purchasingicon" data-udi="umb://media/2e8f4a403baa40158b5cec9b8452dfe5" />
<p style="text-align: center;">Ethical purchasing -</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">Prioritising <a data-udi="umb://document/ea4d933f6e4e4c189eb995e7bf4f1bd4" href="/{localLink:umb://document/ea4d933f6e4e4c189eb995e7bf4f1bd4}" title="Insider's Guide: EcoSki - Interview with founder Rachael">nature-friendly</a> suppliers; reusing and repurposing.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100620/food-250x250.jpg" alt="foodicon" data-udi="umb://media/1ca082bf72344467a4b45a534b647199" />
<p style="text-align: center;">Celebrating Food &amp; Drink -</p>
<p style="text-align: center;">More plant-based ingredients and less food miles. </p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100621/protection-250x250.jpg" alt="protectingicon" data-udi="umb://media/91fac38a338b40138f1e9688747e98f0" />
<p style="text-align: center;">Protection and restoration -</p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/58360366a5274b68b2a6a53bba22ec4d" href="/{localLink:umb://document/58360366a5274b68b2a6a53bba22ec4d}" title="Our Animal Protection Policy">Protecting nature</a> and animals and regenerating biodiversity.</p>
</div>
</div>
<h2>Community</h2>
<p>Engaging and empowering communities</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100618/charity-250x250.jpg" alt="charityicon" data-udi="umb://media/64bf1bc22ebc4ee6be29e9f659e9b7cb" />
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/791fa5aa176246cbbaa02331f3c763ef" href="/{localLink:umb://document/791fa5aa176246cbbaa02331f3c763ef}" title="Partnerships">Charity &amp; Volunteering</a> - Working with charities and volunteering to make a difference on key issues.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100619/conversation-250x250.jpg" alt="customericon" data-udi="umb://media/573c27c9cf754f55ba5a62e700ac9582" />
<p style="text-align: center;">Customer conversation - Inspiring customers to travel more sustainably and responsibly.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow" style="text-align: center;"><img src="/media/13100615/accessibility-250x250.jpg" alt="inclusionicon" data-udi="umb://media/a2b6efc18cee40538617ea2de7d19aad" />
<p style="text-align: center;"><span></span><a data-udi="umb://document/db4567ae70304c2892abca6e930c2def" href="/{localLink:umb://document/db4567ae70304c2892abca6e930c2def}" title="Snow Camp">Inclusion for all</a> - Bettering our holidays so they are fair and just for everyone.</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow"><iframe width="100%" height="400" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/9wR_YGu169c" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>
<p><strong>Committed to Change -</strong> We, along with all our sister brands within the Hotelplan UK Group, are committed to change. Hotelplan UK Group was a signatory and launch partner of the Glasgow Declaration on Climate Action in Tourism. We measure our impact, we reduce our carbon footprint, we want to mitigate negative impacts and we communicate about our progress.</p>
</div>
</div>
<h2 style="text-align: left;">Climate Action Plan</h2>
<p style="text-align: left;">We published our climate action plan in early 2023 which directly addressed our impact and what we are doing to reduce it. In December 2023, we published the results of our second carbon audit and shared how we’re progressing towards our goals</p>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><a data-udi="umb://media/b3e8c2d9ef9643828be3c9a2668aa603" href="/media/13098529/biodiversity-paper-2023.pdf" title="Biodiversity Paper 2023"><img src="/media/13094827/acob023_hotelplan_sustainability-report_biodiversity-paper_01.jpg" alt="Biodiversity 2023" data-udi="umb://media/4b306a37b69d42559c38103fa14648e5" /></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><a data-udi="umb://media/2be48a811a914d2aab475e7ddb2525b0" href="/media/13098530/climate-paper-2023.pdf" title="Climate Paper 2023"><img src="/media/13094828/acob023_hotelplan_sustainability-report_climate-paper_01.jpg" alt="Climate Paper 2023" data-udi="umb://media/c19ee5a404a84c7aa51efdca4f41df03" /></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-4">
<div class="c-card c-card--generic c-card--generic-shadow">
<p><a data-udi="umb://media/441c36f2620b4ced8bfb4dbfe89e93d1" href="/media/13102309/202312-final-hotelplan-uk-protecting-our-futures-planet-and-people-report.pdf" title="Hotelplan UK Protecting Our Futures Planet And People Report"><img src="/media/13102308/hotelplan-uk-protecting-our-futures-front-cover.jpg" alt="People&amp;Planet" data-udi="umb://media/f9b9d0077af34955a23a1973a498b7fe" /></a></p>
</div>
</div>
<p style="text-align: left;">Please contact us on sustainability@hotelplan.co.uk with any feedback or questions you may have regards our sustainability journey.</p>]]></bodyText>
